	<div class="terms terms-inline"><ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_251 first"><a href="/categories/jokes-songs-poems-plays" rel="tag" title="Anything with rhythm and rhyme, anything you can do on a stage, anything you can laugh about, including translations thereof.">Jokes, Songs, Poems &amp; Plays</a></li>
